  "instructions": [
    "1. Preheat grill to medium-high heat.",
    "2. In a large bowl, whisk together berbere spice mix, red wine, garlic, salt, and black pepper.",
    "3. Add the lamb cubes to the bowl and toss to coat with the spice mixture.",
    "4. Thread the lamb onto the skewers, leaving a small space between each cube.",
    "5. Brush the skewers with olive oil.",
    "6. Grill the lamb skewers for 8-10 minutes per side, or until cooked through.",
    "7. Let the skewers rest for 5 minutes before serving."
